The Hav<0xC3><0xAD><0xC5><0x99>ov "deregulation" partition, however, is definitely not overwhelmed with questions.
"Of yesterday's 360 clients, only about forty to fifty people were here because of the 2011 lease," the employee behind the counter estimated.
