The large screen hanging at the ceiling opposite the padded seats of the Hav<0xC3><0xAD><0xC5><0x99>ov waiting room repeats several red highlights.
"The increase in rent in 2011 by 15% or less concerns 31,200 apartments, that is more than 90% of the apartments of the RPG."
"And it will always be at most about 7.50 CZK per square meter and month," he will appear on the screen.
Only 400 apartments from the RPG portfolio will see a 38% increase in rent.
"In these cases, this is an increase from an extremely low amount of CZK 19.66 per square meter," the RPG notes.
